Bruce Smith
Mr. Smith is a Managing Partner and the Chief Investment Officer at Alpha Meridian Capital. He specializes in risk arbitrage strategies and has over 30 years of experience achieving high returns on personal and family assets. Mr. Smith has a Bachelors degree in Finance from The University of Rhode Island.
Tushar Patel
Mr. Patel is a Managing Partner and the Chief Operating Officer at Alpha Meridian Capital. He has extensive business strategy and operational experience as founder of three technology startups as well as a long and accomplished career in private investing, IT advisory, and management consulting services. Mr. Patel has a Masters of Business Administration from The University of Cambridge, UK and a Bachelors degree in Computer Science from The University of Birmingham, UK.







About Us
Alpha Meridian Capital is a private investment partnership specializing in Capital Structure Arbitrage and Special Situations. Our mission is to deliver absolute and consistent returns to our partners year over year.







